

used Command :
   npx json-server -p 3500 -w data/db.json
   to set up JSON rest API.
   db.json is in the data folder 
   data fetching happened from http://localhost:3500/items
   json server code ran in git bash. It can be done in termianl also.

   lenovo@LAPTOP-RO1N9G1U MINGW64 /d/react/reactWithDaveGray (master)
$ npx json-server -p 3500 -w data/db.json
--watch/-w can be omitted, JSON Server 1+ watches for file changes by default
JSON Server started on PORT :3500
Press CTRL-C to stop
Watching data/db.json...

